wiki.summary: "ELEVEN" is a song recorded by South Korean girl group IVE. It was released on December 1, 2021 as the group's debut single from their first single album of the same name. The track was written by Seo Ji-eum, Peter Rycroft (also known as Lostboy), Lauren Aquilina and Ryan S. Jhun, composed by Rycroft, Aquilina and Jhun, and arranged by Rycroft, Jhun and Alawn. A Japanese-language version of the track would later be released on September 19, 2022. Read more on Last.fm.
